prefercite.p: Smithsonian Institution Archives, Accession 95-131, Smithsonian Institution, Office of Physical Plant, Horticulture Services Division, Administrative Files

scopecontent.head: Descriptive Entry
scopecontent.p: These records consist of administrative files. The files contain internal and external memorandum and correspondence concerning grounds and greenhouse maintenance, most of which contain horticulture services. There is correspondence from the Blair House, the National Park Service, the Festival of American Folklife, and the Garden Club of America/Archive of American Garden. Additionally there is some correspondence from Environmental Management and Safety deal with hazardous waste disposal and correspondence regarding the United States Soldier and Airmen's Home. Also included are landscape sketches and drawings, vouchers, invoices, and notes for the FY 1990 and 1991.

userestrict.head: Use Restriction
userestrict.p: Restricted for 15 years, until Jan-01-2009; Transferring office; Contact reference staff for details.
